---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="山の仕事">
<style is:global>
.page-header { max-width: var(--wide); margin: 0 auto; padding: 4rem 1.25rem 3rem; border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--paper-dark); }
.page-eyebrow { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.18em; color: var(--ink-faint); text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
.page-title { font-size: clamp(28px,4vw,44px); font-weight: 400; color: var(--ink); letter-spacing: 0.06em; line-height: 1.3; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
.page-desc { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 300; color: var(--ink-light); line-height: 1.9; max-width: 560px; letter-spacing: 0.02em; }
.page-count { margin-top: 1.5rem; font-size: 11px; color: var(--ink-faint); letter-spacing: 0.08em; }
.job-list { max-width: var(--wide); margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 0 6rem; }
.job-card { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 320px 1fr; border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--paper-dark); cursor: pointer; transition: background 0.2s; }
.job-card:hover { background: var(--paper-mid); }
.job-card:hover .job-img img { transform: scale(1.03); }
.job-img { overflow: hidden; background: var(--paper-dark); aspect-ratio: 4/3; }
.job-img img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; display: block; transition: transform 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.4,0,0.2,1); }
.job-body { padding: 2rem 2rem 2rem 2.5rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; border-left: 0.5px solid var(--paper-dark); }
.job-tags { display: flex; gap: 6px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.job-tag { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1em; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 2px; }
.job-tag-type { background: var(--ink); color: var(--paper); }
.job-tag-area { background: var(--paper-mid); color: var(--ink-light); border: 0.5px solid var(--paper-dark); }
.job-org { font-size: 11px; color: var(--ink-faint); letter-spacing: 0.06em; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
.job-title { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 400; color: var(--ink); line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 0.04em; margin-bottom: 0.875rem; }
.job-story { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 300; color: var(--ink-light); line-height: 1.85; letter-spacing: 0.02em; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; display: -webkit-box; -webkit-line-clamp: 3; -webkit-box-orient: vertical; overflow: hidden; }
.job-info { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px; margin-top: auto; padding-top: 1.5rem; border-top: 0.5px solid var(--paper-dark); }
.job-info-row { display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: baseline; }
.job-info-label { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: var(--ink-faint); text-transform: uppercase; min-width: 56px; flex-shrink: 0; }
.job-info-value { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 300; color: var(--ink-mid); letter-spacing: 0.02em; }
.job-footer { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; margin-top: 1rem; }
.job-read-more { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: var(--ink-faint); border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--paper-dark); padding-bottom: 2px; width: fit-content; transition: color 0.2s; }
.job-card:hover .job-read-more { color: var(--ink); border-color: var(--ink-light); }
@media (max-width: 600px) { .page-header { padding: 2.5rem 1.25rem 2rem; } }
@media (max-width: 720px) {
  .job-card { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .job-img { aspect-ratio: 16/9; }
  .job-body { padding: 1.25rem; border-left: none; border-top: 0.5px solid var(--paper-dark); }
}
</style>

<div class="page-header">
  <div class="page-eyebrow">Jobs</div>
  <h1 class="page-title">山の仕事</h1>
  <p class="page-desc">林業・製材・森林管理——山に関わる仕事を探している人と、人を探している現場を繋ぐ。都市では出会えない仕事が、ここにある。</p>
  <div class="page-count">5 jobs</div>
</div>

<div class="job-list">
  <a href="#" class="job-card fade-in">
    <div class="job-img"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1448375240586-882707db888b?w=800&q=70" alt=""></div>
    <div class="job-body">
      <div class="job-org">有限会社 奥山林業</div>
      <div class="job-title">木を育て、山を守る。<br>林業作業士を募集</div>
      <div class="job-story">「木を切る仕事だと思って来たら、木を育てる仕事だった」——ここで働くスタッフが口を揃えて言う。奥山林業は岐阜県郡上市で60年続く林業会社。</div>
      <div class="job-info">
        <div class="job-info-row"><span class="job-info-label">勤務地</span><span class="job-info-value">岐阜県郡上市（移住支援あり）</span></div>
        <div class="job-info-row"><span class="job-info-label">雇用形態</span><span class="job-info-value">正社員・契約社員</span></div>
        <div class="job-info-row"><span class="job-info-label">給与</span><span class="job-info-value">月給 22万円〜（経験考慮）</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="job-footer">
        <div class="job-tags"><span class="job-tag job-tag-type">林業</span><span class="job-tag job-tag-area">岐阜県</span></div>
        <span class="job-read-more">詳しく見る</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </a>
  <a href="#" class="job-card fade-in">
    <div class="job-img"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1503174971373-b1f69850bded?w=800&q=70" alt=""></div>
    <div class="job-body">
      <div class="job-org">丸木製材所</div>
      <div class="job-title">木の声を聞く職人。<br>製材スタッフ募集</div>
      <div class="job-story">丸太が板になる瞬間がある。鋸が入り、木目が現れる。その瞬間に立ち会える仕事が製材だ。長野県諏訪市の丸木製材所では、国産材にこだわった製材を60年続けてきた。</div>
      <div class="job-info">
        <div class="job-info-row"><span class="job-info-label">勤務地</span><span class="job-info-value">長野県諏訪市</span></div>
        <div class="job-info-row"><span class="job-info-label">雇用形態</span><span class="job-info-value">正社員（未経験歓迎）</span></div>
        <div class="job-info-row"><span class="job-info-label">給与</span><span class="job-info-value">月給 20万円〜</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="job-footer">
        <div class="job-tags"><span class="job-tag job-tag-type">製材</span><span class="job-tag job-tag-area">長野県</span></div>
        <span class="job-read-more">詳しく見る</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </a>
  <a href="#" class="job-card fade-in">
    <div class="job-img"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1545324418-cc1a3fa10c00?w=800&q=70" alt=""></div>
    <div class="job-body">
      <div class="job-org">吉野林業組合</div>
      <div class="job-title">400年の山と向き合う。<br>森林施業プランナー募集</div>
      <div class="job-story">吉野杉は日本を代表するブランド材だ。その山を未来に繋いでいくために、施業計画を立て、所有者と山の橋渡しをする人を求めている。</div>
      <div class="job-info">
        <div class="job-info-row"><span class="job-info-label">勤務地</span><span class="job-info-value">奈良県吉野郡</span></div>
        <div class="job-info-row"><span class="job-info-label">雇用形態</span><span class="job-info-value">正社員</span></div>
        <div class="job-info-row"><span class="job-info-label">給与</span><span class="job-info-value">月給 25万円〜（資格手当あり）</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="job-footer">
        <div class="job-tags"><span class="job-tag job-tag-type">森林管理</span><span class="job-tag job-tag-area">奈良県</span></div>
        <span class="job-read-more">詳しく見る</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </a>
</div>
</Layout>
